Package: rp.flm.test
Type: Package
Title: Goodness-of-fit test for the functional linear model with scalar response based on random projections
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2017-01-10
Authors@R: c(person("Eduardo", "Garcia-Portugues", role = c("aut", "cre"),
		     email = "edgarcia@est-econ.uc3m.es"), person("Manuel", "Febrero-Bande", role = "aut", email = "manuel.febrero@usc.es"))
Description: Goodness-of-fit test for the functional linear model with scalar response based on random projections. The package implements the method described in Cuesta-Albertos et al. (2017).
